{"tid":362060,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"警正式落案控告 林明日缺席聆訊","createTime":"2017-08-16T15:30:09.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-17T02:00:59.000Z","uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5ba0e9a2a88be74b974fae889483d768e828be38","tid":362060,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T15:30:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://media.zenfs.com/en_us/News/singtao/20170816a223104.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen_us%2FNews%2Fsingtao%2F20170816a223104.jpg&h=887ff7ec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【星島日報報道】民主黨成員林子健早前涉嫌以虛假資料誤導警員被捕，被警方扣留兩日後，警方今晚正式落案控告他一項「誤導警務人員」罪，案件將於明日早上在九龍城裁判法院提堂，林子健將缺席聆訊。<br />\n<br />\n林子健昨日深夜在紅磡警署報稱感到頭暈，需送院治理，送往醫院期間需戴上氧氣罩，他其後被推離電腦掃描室，由警員押解前往10樓內科G病房留醫。據悉，林子健報稱頭痛，今日會繼續留院觀察。<br />\n<br />\n林子健上星期報稱被擄走，他昨晨涉嫌以虛假資料誤導警務人員被捕，並通宵扣查。昨午近5時，林子健由女律師陪同，乘坐警方車輛從紅磡警署出發10分鐘後到警方西九龍總部。林子健傍晚7時，乘坐警方車輛離開西九龍總部，被帶返紅磡警署。"},{"pid":"842cac1886ccbc6f6df78ed4ae86871afe7fbe7d","tid":362060,"uid":15711,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T17:02:16.000Z","msg":"之前就識開記招，而家衰左就縮沙"},{"pid":"e08da323619a1bbdd349969997ce99a20214936f","tid":362060,"uid":19196,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T17:07:35.000Z","msg":"泛民集體炒車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0594f7ca4a424d28387e17ce0eb2f70f119e1a9","tid":362060,"uid":117722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T23:26:41.000Z","msg":"想自殺？"},{"pid":"a6a0e6a236680aceac05b313f92cc9e9a7767856","tid":362060,"uid":128594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T01:19:33.000Z","msg":"點解個樣成個智障一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35a4204337247626ee8406623cf4c073ec692f72","tid":362060,"uid":102096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T01:20:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ada9c525d175e094faf3c8367d16e4fb8a3a1930","tid":362060,"uid":61748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T02:00:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"24ba955da29d018d254a88904b9a54dcd73c32e1","tid":362060,"uid":42200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T02:00:59.000Z","msg":"成功轉移視線 香港愚民又比CCTVB玩弄"}]}